Mmino go tewa bodiragatsi jwa tlhamo ya dipina. Go tlwaelesegile gore o tlhodiwe ka diletso tse di farologanyeng go ya le lefatshe le o tlhamelwang go lone le mofuta o go itebaganngwang le one fa o tlhamiwa. Le fa go le jalo, diletso di kgona go tlhoka go dirisiwa ka mabaka a a farologanyeng, mme mo boemong jwa tsone, lenstwe le dirisiwe ga mmogo le dikarolo dingwe  tsa mmele (bogolo jang diatla le dinao) go letsa modumo wa mmino. Godimo ga moo, ga go hakgamatse gore e mengwe e bochwe ka diletso go sena lentswe le le opelang. 

Mmino o kgaogantswe ka mefuta ee malwa. Mo [[Aferika Borwa]] re na le mefuta mengwe e e bidiwang kwaito, Reggae, Gospel, house le pop. Mengwe ya tse, e bua ka dilo tse di diragalang, go gakolola bareetsi, go tlhalosa maikutlo le botshelo jwa motlhami kgotsa a motho wa boemo jwa boraro a dirisiwa a le setshwantsho se moreetsi a nyalanang molaetsa wa mmino le sone.
